{"tid":1465132,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我屌你老母阿死金毛","createTime":"2019-08-13T15:49:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T18:37:43.000Z","uid":156096,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5cda6a27a17cc0e35c20d7f8d23389dee0974097","tid":1465132,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:49:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好同我講有咁多巧合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n首先條仆街仔打自己友，打救護，打立場哥哥已經9成唔係自己友<br />\n第二，條友同身邊幾個人(唔肯定佢地識唔識)不斷咁挑起現場情緒，又話要打死個公安。<br />\n但當情緒高漲時，佢突然走人。過左無耐，黑警就黎左。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果佢咁想公安死，會唔會走人阿?<br />\n第三，明明開頭大家都無衝狗車，條仆街仔突然出黎阻住，好似驚死人無衝咁。<br />\n敢問一句，佢咁勇亞，9成發過夢啦，咁點會唔驚上鏡阿。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8550a239030b5990377a95401e96cc6217763741","tid":1465132,"uid":85708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:37:43.000Z","msg":"屌 依個岩"}]}